17 Jan

1. In uptrend draw support only when new high is created. Mark all resistance
2. In down trend reverse of above.
3. Check for descripency, usually sign of reversal. can be picked for next day trading.

Feb 28

1. Second support is important, check for breakout
2. If second support broken then down trend

If nifty
above Weekly high or low then buy side
below weekly low then buy or sell
